---
title: Chilli Prawn & Chorizo Jambalaya Rice with Sour Cream & Parsley
description: Satisfy your cravings for bold, vibrant flavours with this Louisiana staple! Succulent prawns and chorizo mingle with aromatic rice and veggies to create a hearty dish full of savoury flavours. A dollop of sour cream on top is the perfect cooling accompaniment.
